name: Osaka
description:
Very rarely, you can catch the water of Dotonbori this calm. Like a perfect mirror.
The photo was taken and edited circa 2009.

About the artist:
Tokyoluv is a visual artist and street photographer who crafts lush, cyberpunk-inspired shots of cities. For over a decade, his photos have been enjoyed by millions across the world with his pieces perfectly capturing the neon look of a bustling city at night.
